    "media:imagetext": "AIR\nCALIFORNIA 737s\nWe're easy to take.\nSaving\nFLIGHT\nSCHEDULE\nEffective January 2, 1975\nIf there's\nan easier way\nto get you there,\nwe'll be\nthe first to\ntell you.\nCALIFORNIA\nSunjets\nare the easy way to\nSacramento, San Francisco,\nOakland, San Jose, Palm\nSprings, Ontario, Orange\nCounty, San Diego.\nWe think our schedule will match\nyour schedule. But if you have any\nquestions about the easiest way to\ntravel among our eight major\nregional airports, call Air California\nEasy Information. Phone numbers\nare listed inside...",
